News Website
This is a news website project that uses HTML, CSS, and JavaScript to display news articles from various sources. The website is built using the NewsAPI, which provides access to a wide range of news articles from different categories, including cricket and more.

Features
Displays news articles from various sources
Categorizes news articles into different categories, including cricket
Allows users to read full articles by clicking on the headlines
Provides a clean and responsive user interface
Supports mobile and desktop devices
Technologies Used
HTML
CSS
JavaScript
Getting Started
To get started with the project, follow these steps:

Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/MayurPondkule/global-news.git
Open the project folder.
Open index.html in your web browser to view the website.
Configuration
The project uses the NewsAPI to fetch news articles. To configure the API access, follow these steps:

Sign up for an account at NewsAPI.
Obtain an API key from your NewsAPI account.
Open script.js file.
Replace YOUR_API_KEY with your actual NewsAPI key.